Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_int_info3

This register contains the retry response associated with the RTRY_ERR interrupt. The register is only updated when the RTRY_ERR is initially detected. Once the interrupt is cleared then additional information can be captured.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
